text:
I can't speak Russian yet. I used Google translate to get a ticket from the queue machine then I found the right table for opening my account in Ceber Bank. The staff couldn't speak English but they were very kind, careful and patient. By Google  translate I could tell them that I need to open an account and they  also were asking me their questions using another translator. 
They even helped me to add money by ATM/CDM machine. all jobs done with help of bank staff.
